features: Stationery Set for Writing Letters - You will receive 64 sheets of writing letter paper,comes in 8 assorted fancy designs,include purple flowers, starry sky, night forest, botanical garden, black cat piano, blue flowers, feather themes. This premium thick gold stamping lined paper set is printed on one sided paper and golden printing border on the head and bottom, which is lovely and elegant, easy to add a personal touch to surprise your love one.

Excellent Quality Writing Paper - Lined paper made of premium smooth paper for durability, thick and sturdy, handwriting friendly and printer friendly that can perfectly meet your handwriting or printing needs.

Easily Personalized - Each sheet of watercolor floral border paper has a sizable blank space to add personalized text,stickers,picture,messages and so on, the unique border and flower edges can create more lovely vibes.

Wide Application - These cute letter papers are not only for writing letters,you can use this stationary paper to write down new year wishes to your friends and family members.In addition,It can be also used as greeting cards or invitation for halloween party,christmas party,old-fashioned style weddings,anniversaries,graduation and birthday party.
Size and Quantity - letter paper size:5.62 x 8.26 Inch/143 x 210 mm,comes in 8 assorted fancy border designs, 8 of each, 64 sheets in total.
